Hardware e Periferiche

Qualcomm, i nuovi Snapdragon X2 Elite, Extreme e Snapdragon 8 Elite Gen 5 destinati a PC e smartphone

Di Mauro Notarianni

25 Set 2025

<img 
                                        fetchpriority="high" 
                                        width="741" 
                                        height="486" 
                                        class="entry-thumb" 
                                        src="https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2025/09/spandragon8elite-741x486.jpg.webp" srcset="https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2025/09/spandragon8elite-741x486.jpg.webp 741w,  https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2025/09/spandragon8elite-50x34.jpg.webp 50w" sizes="(max-width: 741px) 100vw, 741px" 
